Interface Context.Builder

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    Context.Builder.Base
    Enclosing interface:
    Context

    public static interface Context.Builder
    A builder of a Context object.

    Values created by ValueFactory's will be added to this object and then build() method will be called by FruitJuice's framework.
